name: Mercer
poll_display_race: Polls close at 8 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Mail ballots were sent to all active, registered voters, and those postmarked by Election Day have until Nov. 10 to arrive. All in-person voters cast provisional ballots, which will be counted beginning Nov. 10. It took weeks to finish counting ballots during the state's July primary.
